column1: #Text=R WOOD WARD, Printer, Bookbinder, • and Stationer, 69, St.

#Text=Mary Street, impressed with gratitude for the numerous favours conferred on him since his commencement as above, begs to offer his sincere acknowledgments ; and earnestly hopes, that by embracing every improvement, strict assiduity, and reasonable charges, lie shall ensure a share of public patronage in future.
#Text=Printing of every description expeditiously executed in the best style.
#Text=Orders for Periodical Publications punctually procured Advertisements received for, and transmitted to any Xcwsjmper in the United Kingdom.
